    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="grid__item width-one-half">
        <h3>What if my charge came outside of Florida?</h3>
        <p>This is only for Convicts who had a charge in Florida.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid__item width-one-half">
        <h3>What if I haven't paid off what I owe to government?</h3>
        <p>You need to pay that before you can vote.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>